.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTPAYS-COMPLETE-FEE-TOTAL" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listpays-complete-fee-total \- FEAT-2181 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listpays-complete-fee-total
.SH DESCRIPTION
verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2181).
.PP
Reports the total routing fees paid across all complete payments, derived from the difference between amount_sent_msat and amount_msat.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
